a:5:{s:5:"title";s:64:"Salesmate Smart Flows add automated emails to deal participants";s:16:"text-format-info";a:3:{s:10:"text-final";s:383:"<p>Salesmate introduced a Smart Flows action to email deal participants, reducing manual follow-ups and keeping stakeholders aligned.</p>
<p>Where to find it: Smart Flows → Actions → Send Email to Deal Participants.</p>
<p>Learn more here: <a href="https://www.salesmate.io/blog/january-2026-release-notes/">https://www.salesmate.io/blog/january-2026-release-notes/</a></p>
